Packaging and branding specialist agency Berge Farrell wanted to shake up a movement to elevate and re-engage an iconic brand with its audience. “We are excited to work on a truly South African brand with a rich history and tell its authentic story in the relaunch,” says Managing Director, Andrew Nel. Berge Farrell brings the right expertise to the table to help strengthen the position of this much-loved brand.<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1804/438698-625x446.jpg" alt="Account win for Berge Farrell" width="625" height="446">